Main Idea:
    This project is supposed to replicate a game of 15-puzzle, where the goal of the game is to arrage the board such
    that all numbers are ordered from 1-15 properly, moving 1 tile at a time.

Classes Needed:
    Main:
        * Prints out

    Board:
        * Holds the board layout of the game.
        * Update board values when requested.
        * Convert board to a String value.

        - Mover

    Mover:
        * Request move input from user.
        * Check if move input is valid.
        * Send move input to Board.

        - Console
        - Board